  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create a trap made to capture creatures who enter the traps space.</p><p>This trap is set on a 5-foot space.</p><p>All creatures within 10 feet of this trap when it is triggered makes its saving throw being grappled and restrained on a failed save.</p><p>A creature who fails their saving throw by 5 or more, is stunned and paralyzed until the end of their next turn, and afterwards grappled and restrained for the next minute.</p><p>Creatures restrained or grappled in this way, remakes this save at the end of each of their turns ending effects on a pass.</p><p></p><p>Build DC: 15</p><p>Notice/Disable DC: 16</p><p>Toolkit Req to create/disable: Trappers kit + Battle Wire</p>",
